reer goals are about more than job titles – they’re about making a positive impact.\nMay 17, 2024 Article People Stories Early Careers Hub -\nMeet Sam\nLike many young people, Sam wasn’t sure what she wanted to do with her life. It turned out, cybersecurity was the missing piece of the puzzle.\nMay 17, 2024 Article People Stories Early Careers Hub -\nMeet Tosin\nHe’s a technology graduate within the chief technology office, having recently moved from the consumer banking payments unit.\nMay 17, 2024 Article People Stories Early Careers Hub -\nHear about Jamie's journey on our Tech Apprenticeship and beyond\nFrom a life-changing decision at the age of 15, to developing solutions that change people’s lives by the time he was 21, Jamie’s journey has been full of incredible achievements.\nMay 23, 2024 Article People Stories Early Careers Hub -\nMeet Lisa Murphy\nMeet Lisa Murphy our Head of Europe Climate Risk, Paris\nJune 10, 2024 Blog People Stories Hub -\nMeet Adam Last\nMeet Adam Last, Head of Cash Sales, Amsterdam\nJune 10, 2024 Blog People Stories Hub -\nEmployee Stories\nMeet Alaoishe Luskin, Head of Recovery & Resolution Planning, Dublin\nJune 11, 2024 -\nMeet Ambarish Phanse\nMeet Ambarish Phanse, Equity Derivatives Trader, Frankfurt\nJune 11, 2024 -\nTechnology Spotlight\nOpportunities that just keep getting bigger and better\nJanuary 10, 2024 Article People Stories Tech Related Content - Tech -\nLouis, Assistant Vice President\nHear how Louis grew his career in a culture that puts people first\nMarch 05, 2024 Article People Stories Hub -\nReimagining data\nBig data, big impact. It's happening here\nMay 24, 2024 Article Tech Related Content - Tech -\nMeet Corinne Grain\nMeet Corinne Grain, Paris, Markets\nJune 20, 2024 Blog People Stories Hub -\nEmployee Resource Group\nEvolve is our midlife progression ERG that supports all colleagues' evolving life-stages and career progression.\nJune 20, 2024 -\nNatacha Dervisevic, Credit Trader, Markets\nNatacha talks with